## 5. Built-In Games

### ♟️ Chess
- Interactive board rendered in the browser (e.g., `react-chessboard` + `chess.js`)
- Legal move validation with Stockfish WASM
- Dual countdown timers synced via WebSocket
- Move history sidebar
- Eye-tracking via webcam + MediaPipe in browser
- Resign button

### 🧠 Quiz
- 10 randomized multiple-choice questions
- Per-question countdown timer
- Progress bar ("Question 3 of 10")
- Eye-tracking via webcam
- Auto-advance after answer selection

### 💪 Push-ups
- Webcam feed via `getUserMedia()` / WebRTC
- Real-time rep counter using MediaPipe Pose (WASM, runs in browser)
- Opponent's rep count synced via WebSocket
- Match countdown timer
- Background verification (single user, no devices)
- Random gesture liveness challenge

---

## 6. User-Created Games

Any user can build a custom game and publish it. When others play it, the **creator earns 5% of every match pot**.

### Revenue Split — Custom Games
```
Total Pot (e.g., €20 = €10 × 2 players)
    ├── Winner:   85%  →  €17.00
    ├── Platform: 10%  →  €2.00
    └── Creator:   5%  →  €1.00
```

> Built-in games (Chess, Quiz, Push-ups) use 85% winner / 15% platform.

### Creation Flow
1. User opens "Create Game" page
2. Fills template: title, description, category, game type, rules/questions, assets, difficulty, bet range
3. Previews and tests the game
4. Submits for moderation
5. Moderator approves → game goes live in the marketplace
6. Other users discover, play, and rate it
7. Creator earns 5% royalties on every match automatically

### Supported Game Types
| Type | Description | Example |
|---|---|---|
| `quiz` | Multiple-choice Q&A | "Football Trivia" — 10 questions |
| `trivia` | Speed knowledge round | "Science Speed Round" |
| `challenge` | Task-based scoring | "Memory Match" — find pairs |
| `physical` | Webcam-verified activity | "Plank Hold" — longest hold wins |

### Game Template (JSON)
```json
{
  "title": "Football Trivia",
  "game_type": "quiz",
  "category": "sports",
  "difficulty": "medium",
  "min_bet": 5,
  "max_bet": 50,
  "rules": {
    "question_count": 10,
    "time_per_question": 15,
    "scoring": "correct_answer_1pt",
    "tiebreaker": "speed",
    "questions": [
      {
        "text": "Who won the 2022 FIFA World Cup?",
        "options": ["Brazil", "France", "Argentina", "Germany"],
        "correct": 2
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

### Creator Dashboard
| Metric | Description |
|---|---|
| Total Plays | Times the game has been played |
| Total Earnings | Cumulative 5% royalties |
| Average Rating | 1–5 stars |
| Recent Matches | Last 10 matches |
| Weekly Trend | Play count over time |

