## 7. Anti-Cheat System

Anti-cheat runs **in the browser** using the user's webcam via WebRTC + MediaPipe WASM.

| Layer | Method | Trigger |
|---|---|---|
| Liveness | Random gesture (blink, nod, smile) within 5s | Match start |
| Eye-tracking | Gaze deviation >30° for >2s | Chess/Quiz — 3 warnings = forfeit |
| Pose estimation | 33 landmarks, >20% displacement per rep | Push-ups/Physical |
| Background | Color variance <10%, 1 human, no devices | All webcam games |

All violations are logged server-side to `anti_cheat_logs`.

---

## 8. Payment & Escrow

### Token Purchase
```
User selects amount (€5–€100)  →  Stripe Checkout  →  Webhook confirms  →  Tokens credited
```

### Escrow
```
Player creates challenge  →  Bet locked from wallet
Opponent joins            →  Their bet locked too
Match plays               →  Winner determined
Payout:
  • Built-in game:  85% winner / 15% platform
  • Custom game:    85% winner / 10% platform / 5% creator
```

---

## 9. Real-Time Sync

Via **Supabase Realtime WebSocket**.

| Event | Latency Target |
|---|---|
| `match:opponent_found` | <500ms |
| `match:move` | <100ms |
| `match:answer` | <100ms |
| `match:score_update` | <200ms |
| `match:completed` | <500ms |
| `match:forfeited` | <500ms |

