## 11. Security & Compliance

| Area | Measure |
|---|---|
| Transit encryption | TLS 1.3 |
| At-rest encryption | AES-256 |
| Password hashing | bcrypt (12 rounds) |
| Sessions | JWT, 24-hour expiry |
| Payment data | PCI DSS via Stripe (zero card storage) |
| KYC/AML | Email + phone verification |
| Rate limiting | 100 req/min, 10 matches/hr, 5 payments/hr |
| GDPR | Data deletion, consent management |
| Fraud | Duplicate detection, betting patterns, 24hr withdrawal hold |
| Game moderation | User-created games require approval before publishing |

---

