## 13. Future Roadmap

### 🔴 High Priority
- **Leaderboards & Rankings** — Global + per-game, ELO skill rating, weekly resets
- **Tournament Mode** — Bracket elimination, prize pools, scheduled starts
- **Social Features** — Friends, private challenges, chat, post-match reactions

### 🟡 Medium Priority
- **Achievement Badges** — Milestones, profile display, bonus rewards
- **Spectator Mode** — Live viewing of public matches
- **Replay System** — Stored replays, social sharing, dispute review
- **Notifications** — Email/browser push for match results, weekly digest
- **Seasonal Events** — Limited-time modes, higher payouts, community goals
- **Mobile App** — React Native port after web MVP is validated

### 🟢 Lower Priority
- **Streaming Integration** — Twitch/YouTube Live, highlight clips
- **AI Features** — LLM quiz generation, post-match coaching, ML anomaly detection
- **Corporate/Team Challenges** — B2B product, company tournaments
- **Marketplace** — Cosmetics (avatar frames, themes, celebration effects)

